section.styleguide-module-details
  h2 Button Groups

  h3 Usage
  dl.styleguide-usage
    dt Wrapper
    dd Button groups are intended to group together primary and secondary buttons. To create a group of buttons wrap them in the class #{inline_code(".button-group")}.
    dt Primary Actions
    dd Primary actions may contain more than one button and are displayed on the right hand side. They should contain only one primary button. If there is more than one button then the primary button should be the furthest to the right. A primary action can be created by wrapping a button or group of buttons with the class #{inline_code(".primary-actions")}.
    dt Secondary Actions
    dd Secondary actions may contain more than one button and are displayed on the left hand side. They should not contain a primary button. A secondary action can be created by wrapping a button or group of buttons with the class #{inline_code(".secondary-actions")}.

